text: John Swaab (28 October 1928 - 4 December 2016) was a Dutch equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1928 births Category:2016 deaths Category:Dutch male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of the Netherlands Category:Equestrians at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Amsterdam
